ish operation, respectively, would fail.","pos":[24281,24490]},{"content":"Now, if a package is in-use the operation will be pended.","pos":[24496,24553]},{"content":"The un-publish and publish-pend operations will be processed on service restart or if another publish or un-publish command is issued.","pos":[24554,24688]},{"content":"In the latter case, if the virtual application is in-use otherwise, the virtual application will remain in a pending state.","pos":[24689,24812]},{"content":"For globally published packages, a restart (or service restart) often needed.","pos":[24813,24890]},{"content":"In a non-persistent environment, it is unlikely these pended operations will be processed.","pos":[24892,24982]},{"content":"The pended operations, for example tasks are captured under <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>HKEY<ph id=\"ph1\">\\_</ph>CURRENT<ph id=\"ph2\">\\_</ph>USER<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph3\">\\\\</ph> <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Software<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph4\">\\\\</ph> <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Microsoft<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph5\">\\\\</ph> <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>AppV<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph6\">\\\\</ph> <bpt id=\"p5\">**</bpt>Client<ept id=\"p5\">**</ept> <ph id=\"ph7\">\\\\</ph> <bpt id=\"p6\">**</bpt>PendingTasks<ept id=\"p6\">**</ept>.","pos":[24983,25146]},{"content":"Although this location is persisted by the UPM solution, if it is not applied to the environment prior to log on, it will not be processed.","pos":[25147,25286]},{"pos":[25322,25390],"content":"Enhancing the VDI Experience through Performance Optimization Tuning"},{"content":"The following section contains lists with information about Microsoft documentation and downloads that may be useful when optimizing your environment for performance.","pos":[25392,25558]},{"content":".NET NGEN Blog and Script (Highly Recommended)","pos":[25562,25608]},{"content":"About NGEN technology","pos":[25612,25633]},{"content":"How to speed up NGEN optimaztion","pos":[25640,25672